<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-11-12T13:41:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-11-12T13:41:00-05:00" n="209" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d209">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.00/650</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Minister in the Netherlands</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_GJW1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Garrett</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">The Hague</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-11-12T19:00:00+00:19">
                                    <hi rend="italic">November 12, 1917, 7 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                                <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 8.30 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>1619. Russian Chargé d’Affaires says that all Russian diplomatic missions
                            in western Europe, with one exception not heard from, have communicated
                            with each other and agreed not to recognize <persName corresp="#p_LNVU1">Lenin</persName> government nor to carry out any instructions that
                            may be received from it.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_GJW1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Garrett</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>